{"tid":1782596,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益-關於連儂牆問題","createTime":"2019-12-14T05:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T06:00:18.000Z","uid":208505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d46e95f1d7469b193616db0990b8f4aa74285442","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得文宣同連儂牆係必須<br />\n否則運動好易比人遺忘</span><br />\n基於有d區好少文宣組<br />\n就算有市民有心想整連儂牆都怕比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n其實我地區選大勝17區<br />\n我地可唔可以提議自己區議員係自己區<br />\n增設一個<span style=\"color: red;\">合法連儂牆</span><br />\n因為我住果區，最近我果邊文宣組唔見晒人影<br />\n區選前日日都更新連儂牆，區選後就冇更新到<br />\n自己都想痴埋文宣，但一條友又怕比狗咬。<br />\n有見及此 想大家集思廣益 假如係自己區都成功增設<br />\n合法連儂牆 咁手足們咪唔洗再比狗咬 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因我立法會每年都有款項比區議會做民生建設</span><br />\n我想大家一齊討論下  方法可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8a97056c9f8188eeb1a4ea5760121ee2cbd955","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f5c0d84af5847be2753350de23c7b9dbaa265b7","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54da70359cfe9533bcdf4968806a8360881406a3","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c2e668f3355b085f08e88d1c95ac859adedf810","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c070647ceaf3c5702ccd8dcc5fc089703d68e576","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"有冇可以同我討論下  方法可唔可行？"},{"pid":"1aecddf834542b5a13154cdc04d43d04f24ec9f0","tid":1782596,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\