 />\n因為佢係屬於區議員既財物<br />\n各大部門都冇得理<br />\n2.繼續吹雞去痴文宣<br />\n自己組隊（又歸於點）有機會比狗咬"},{"pid":"ad2697cc33a6fee4186511b14254baa9db35fdff","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"981150f6e23874440f1977ead0159d781f4b861c","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9e73c6380a99880276da90a747ce698c8bb5084","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0edbe43d8f0fabe77bd5fd70856402560d736f20","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6743f5cd0ea12cb7c06e62f696fc273b30ea62c6","tid":1782596,"uid":295153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"粉嶺火車站比人清左了"},{"pid":"fcb27d37258bfb45ccc5f79340e9684ebb87715e","tid":1782596,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a494c001935aea2cf588c78d3fa958a8c703ae7","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6743f5cd0ea12cb7c06e62f696fc273b30ea62c6","tid":1782596,"uid":295153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"粉嶺火車站比人清左了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"佢地呢幾日全港清洗文宣  <br />\n琴日順利邨文宣組<br />\n成條Team 比狗咬"},{"pid":"d8d646545ce85aeea44fd8322b86c65df141eba8","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"a658fbbe58ef98d6866e16ec44a7eea2018a8826","tid":1782596,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩問左某區「準區議員」  大家傾左15min<br />\n佢話假如用過半議席Pass左「合法連儂牆」<br />\n其實就唔難,最麻煩係後者<br />\n如要興建一個地方都係要立法會撥款，立法會有機會唔批<br />\n同埋佢地會將「合法連儂牆」<br />\n申報上去叫「民主牆」<